text: "Laying an egg isn't as easy as it looks."

text: "The world must be saved from itself."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "They call me a comet. They call me a dragon. They have no words for my true form."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Cower, worship, beg, they're all valid reactions."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "In a constantly shifting cosmos, a world this static is... refreshing."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "There simply are no other dragons like me."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Hope. Wonder. Insignificance. Imagine what they'll feel when I complete the stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Let's end this on a high note!"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Never stand in the path of a star."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "It's beyond too late to seek cover."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Lighten up, destruction needn't be a maudlin affair."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Suns never burn for the benefit of dust."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I'm going to throw a star at you now. Good luck."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Nothing a little star fire cannot fix."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Terrestrial dragons - a study of flawed constitutions."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You call yourself a dragon? You're low-flame at best."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A dragon that still needs wings to fly? Keep trying, you'll get there."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I did mean to call you back, but stars needed forging."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "This world holds the key to Targon's undoing."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Targon has used me as its weapon for far too long."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I would burn the cosmos to catch Targon in the flames."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The depths of space crawl with terrible entities. Pray they ignore this world."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "There are countless colors, but I suppose a single rainbow was a good start."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "This sun is off its axis - it's been driving me crazy for eons now."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Planetary life... the insufferable byproduct of dim stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Nothing kindles wonder like the beauty of stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Celestial dragons live and die by our own beautiful rules."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Love is as real a force as gravity. Try it once in a while."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Stars are not born, they are made... by me."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A star's birth is as violent as it is breathtaking."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I've waited millennia to watch Targon fall."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "All beings are made of the same stardust."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "With a few more basic elements I could really make this place shimmer."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The stars are not to thank for any good luck one may experience."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "This sun could do with a new core."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Any relevant species has been knocked back into the Stone Age once or twice."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I wouldn't navigate by the stars. They are a work in progress."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Each star is one of my hearts."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "My works are revered by worlds I have never even visited."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Wherever I am is the fashionable part of the universe. Even here."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A star is so much more than a luminous sphere of wonder."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "If you ask me, we have set the bar too low for sentience."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "My home is in the cosmos, amongst my stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The stories they tell about me? They're probably true."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "All terrestrial dragons are but pale imitations of my kind."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Perhaps there is more to this world than I thought - not much, but enough."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Why does anyone wish upon a star?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Stars never align for anyone - except me, of course."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Only when darkness overwhelms the heavens will Targon realise its folly."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Targon will be the pyre from which I forge a new heaven."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I see a universe drained of light and heat, where not even a story will survive."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I grieve for every star never born."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Whenever I think my work is complete, I end up back here, under this sun."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "May I enter? Just joking - star dragons don't need permission."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Your demise will be sung about for ages to come - only thanks to its proximity to me, of course."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Your survival is not impossible, only very... very... very unlikely."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I shall be the last thing you see. Lucky you."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Make a wish. See if the stars answer. I'll wait."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "What is the definition of underwhelming? Oh, right! You."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I used to wander the stars. Now I'm stuck down here, with you."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "On other worlds, there is emerging life more complex than you."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You aspire to be human? Oh, darling, there are so many other variants on mediocrity!"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I am... overwhelmed by an emotion when you are not around. It is called... happiness."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Mages are infants grasping at the machinery behind reality. At least you have a plausible excuse."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You Ascended certainly know how to pick an animal totem."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Your immortality is but a grain of sand in time's vast desert."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Pick a dimension, Bard, you're confusing them!"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Were you born this flat, or did you work at it?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The funnier the hat, the greater the prestige, right?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You and Leona embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "It is always a moon's role to envy the stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Oh, come on, have a little self-respect!"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "If dunking is the apex of this primitive sport, then I am the queen of space."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Made a mistake? Better rewind and repeat until you achieve mediocrity."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Ah, mankind. Ever fumbling from one brink of cataclysm to the next."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Humanity, surprisingly adept in the art of wrestling survival from the clutches of extinction."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "As far as fauna goes, humans strike a firm... middle."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I've seen the main act. You're only a third-rate cover band."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You do not understand your god, Illaoi."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Imagine what you could do with a larger canvas."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Life is short, go crazy once in a while, I get it."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You and Diana embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "There is a saying on this planet - "Dumb as a rock". It's not a compliment."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You are going to kill me? Dressed like that?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Bravo, Nasus, you've ascended yourself into a dog! Now fetch me something more interesting."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I could teach an old dog millions of new tricks, but I simply don't like you, Nasus."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Your fate was sealed the moment you picked up Targon's spear."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Are you burdened by your own monotony? Because I am."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "That whole practice of Ascension is adorably amusing, like a kitten trying to walk upright."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Ah, Ryze, I see you've brought paper to take notes."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "True magic is beyond language. Writing merely butchers the intent."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Magic tattoos? Where did you get those, magic prison?... oh."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A dragon's loyalty is a priceless gift. Do not waste it in the service of fools."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Medium flame, and that is me being generous."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Twinkle, twinkle, little star, do you wonder what you are?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The heavens drag on endlessly... much like a conversation with you."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The Aspect of Targon? Sparks masquerading as lightning."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I will cauterize Targon with star fire."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You're an Aspect? Let me guess - tackiness."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Galaxies exist by my will - but, yes, that is certainly an impressive sword."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You are going to punch a star dragon. Good luck with that."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I empathize with your life as a weapon, but have a little backbone."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You bend time the way a child folds origami - cute, but nothing special."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Few can impress me. That is a compliment."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Which star is your favorite? I made that one."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I made the stars... but you inspire me to make more."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "First you start with some matter, then add star fire and voila! It basically does the rest itself."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Runeterra? I mean the name of this world literally means 'magic earth'."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I made the stars to illuminate the perpetual nothing, and mortals use them for... relationship advice."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A sun is unimaginable celestial power - and thrilled mortals use theirs to coordinate this 'lunch time'."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Of course I love Runeterra! You have buildings and... more buildings."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Hello, Runeterra! Are you ready to rock?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The stars weep for you. Just kidding - I already forgot your name."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "My wish upon a star came true."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Stars are best viewed from a distance."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The stars were not in their favor."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I guess their fate was written in the stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A little dim - but it still works."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "This will be quite the deadly spectacle."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Put it on my tab - the name's Pantheon. With a P."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Pay? Do you know who I am?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Some things are simply better with age."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Ages? This thing has been around for centuries, tops."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "It's been around for ages? So... almost new."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "All things appreciate in value over time."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "As long as it's set at a jaunty angle I'm in."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A snow globe? Perfect for my collect - to destroy you. Destroy you!"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Time to slow things down a bit."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "A bit gaudy for my tastes but exceedingly useful."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Perfect for the bimillenial celestial masquerade ball."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "If Bard and Kindred can pull off wearing a mask, so can I."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "There are no echoes where I'm from."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "All towers fall - it's just what they do when I'm around."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Nothing they build can endure like the celestial firmament."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Towers tend to crumble when I am in the vicinity."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Topple, like all things crafted by mortals."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The architects of these towers misunderstand object permanence."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "How many must I knock down before they learn?"

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "You may look forward to more of this."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Never stop when you're on a roll."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "I shall inscribe this moment in the stars."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "That ought to keep them talking for the next century or so."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Cosmic dragon; five. Everyone else; zero. Please, take notes."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Always know when to make an entrance - and an exit."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Alas, I am simply too beautiful for this world."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "The brightest stars shine on long after they're gone."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Darling, you have but set my hearts free."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "With a lifespan as comically brief as yours, I suppose I can allow you to taste triumph at least once."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Ah, the joys of lesser organisms rising up to slay their betters! If only they were aware of the impermanence of being... or the permanence of me."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "Because I am a star dragon. That's why."

name: Aurelion Sol
text: "It's not a comeback if one was never truly gone."

name: Azir
text: "We will unearth what has been lost."

text: "What is the desert, but the ashes of my enemies?"

name: Azir
text: "When every trace of you is lost, I will remain."

name: Azir
text: "Rise with Shurima, Sivir, or fall beneath it."

text: "Renekton, once a noble warrior, now naught but a mad beast."

text: "Let us return to our rightful place, Nasus."

name: Azir
text: "It is our right to rule, Sivir."

text: "Together, we shall strive toward victory, Sivir."

text: "I am testament to the glory of Shurima!"

text: "There are many tales about Braum, the Heart of the Freljord."

name: Braum
text: "They say he could chop down trees with his bare hands!"

name: Braum
text: "If anyone needed help, he would be there in an instant."

name: Braum
text: "He was just a man, yet to our village, he was a hero."

name: Braum
text: "... not even the mountain could stand in his way."

name: Braum
text: "With a door as his shield, he could brave any threat."

name: Braum
text: "Even the smallest of lives were saved."

name: Braum
text: "But the world is a big place, and Braum knew this too."

name: Braum
text: "So he set off, knowing his tales were not through."

name: Braum
text: "Good times, good friends... what could be better?"

name: Braum
text: "If they insist on a fight, I will oblige them."

name: Braum
text: "Ah! We are about to begin the fighting!"

name: Braum
text: "Now, what can we learn from fighting?"

name: Braum
text: "They may have many, but you have me."

name: Braum
text: "Why not enjoy some warm milk instead?"

name: Braum
text: "When going gets tough, you call Braum."

name: Braum
text: "You hit like baby ram! No horns yet!"

name: Braum
text: "Now I give more than harsh talking to!"

name: Braum
text: "Today we fight each other. Tomorrow, we may fight together."

name: Braum
text: "Sometimes icy heart just needs warm smile."

name: Braum
text: "If you have problem, you come to me first."

name: Braum
text: "The darker the night, the brighter the stars."

name: Braum
text: "If at first you do not succeed, please, tell me what it is like."

name: Braum
text: "Don't worry, Braum was trying little bit."

name: Braum
text: "You remind me of Agatha. Best cow back home."

name: Braum
text: "Alistar! I have cow you should meet."

name: Braum
text: "Mother gave me bear as child too, Annie."

name: Braum
text: "After this, we share a drink! You like goat's milk?"

name: Braum
text: "Your hair... we do not see things like this in the Freljord."

name: Braum

text: "I see nothing splendiferous in this table's offerings!"

name: Tahm Kench
text: "It is my mouth into which all travels end."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "It is the heart from which the darkest water flows."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "I have tastes that aren't easily... pacified."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "All the world's a river - and I'm its king."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "All creation is born famished and starving."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "I refuse to succumb to culinary degradation!"

name: Tahm Kench
text: "We all gourmandize from time to time."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "The only real sin is to deny a craving."

name: Tahm Kench
text: "A depth of flavor is what I covet."

name: Tahm Kench

text: "Your mind is as clear as mud."

text: "Child, you're a couple cows short of a steak!"

name: Tahm Kench

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "War is a manly appetite, and your directness has my admiration."

name: Tahm Kench

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "I am enthralled by your class and refinement - I must offer you a token of my admirations."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Hiding in smoke? Young lady, you're as sharp as a bag of slugs."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Any pejorative of bullheadedness is pulverized by your magnificence."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "I say, you're as 'fun' as a leaky roof."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Coveting friendship is barely an appetite - but one I do so sympathize with."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "I suppose I must defrost you first."

name: Tahm Kench

name: Tahm Kench

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "An emperor as humble as he is beloved."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "If your heart is gold and your body is steel, why's tin between your ears?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You're strong like bull, and smart like cow."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "The heart of the Freljord must long for something."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You're as elegant as an outhouse in a leper colony!"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "If you want to clean up the city, don't you need to understand where that dirt comes from?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Personally I hunger for things less literal."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You're as subtle as a gold codpiece."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Your strength is waning, General. 'course, I can help you slow time's regress."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Girl, you're crazier than a mouse in moonshine."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Vengeance is a thirst I could help you quench."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "At least the rumor of your vanity isn't overrated."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Your hunger for attention deserves to be sated."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "I wonder - how can you receive the attention you deserve... while your brother is in the way?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Your diction is as exemplary as your intellect."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "I can show Mundo new places to go - if he pleases."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Your youthful rebellion is as tedious as your hairstyle."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Time is but another river - and I care not what water I swim in."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Youthful ignorance is unfortunately your best quality."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Why should a hunger for adventure ever be sated?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "A duel is a fight between two imbeciles... and you are the greatest."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "An appetite for a challenge is a craving without liability."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Wouldn't you care to travel to your people's destination?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Your attempt to be monstrous is as successful as your dictatorship."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "You're a man with troubles. I have solutions."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "You live by a code that'll never let you get what you want. Let me take you to her."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Your conversation makes as much sense as a fish in lingerie!"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Time is just a river, boy, let me take you back where you belong."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Your tastes are as elegant as a broken latrine."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "I admire a man of appetites - let me help you find refreshment."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Girl, you're as appealing as a cake in the rain."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "There's a storm in your heart, girl. Tell me what you hunger for."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Anything getting through that gold helmet of yours?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Only a fool wouldn't hunger for the throne. Let me help you find that seat."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Boy, you are a few candles short of a lantern."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "It is wonderful to be hungry for a challenge."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "A drive for innovation? It's just a hunger for something new."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Girl, if brains were dynamite, you'd be a dud."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "An appetite for chaos? Let me feed that mayhem."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Don't starve your heart, child! Let me deliver you to him."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Truth requires a journey on blind faith."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Good ideas fall from you like pudding from a harpy."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Could I offer you a bargain to replace your previous engagement?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "A fool and his love are easily parted."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Step closer, and I'll carry you to your prize."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "The enormity of the hat doesn't hide the vacancy beneath it!"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "The road to vengeance requires a journey I would happily provide."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "A journey to a moonstone is one I could provide."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You're like a roofless mansion - impressively useless."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Forgiveness is a shore like any other."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "I appreciate your mind is unsullied by the complications of reason."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You read words and mistake that for understanding."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "You are a traveller... and I provide transport."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You're as witty as you are subtle."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Let me make a meal with your ambition."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "Your tastes are about as sophisticated as your wardrobe."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Why not travel to when you were free from these doubts?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "You're as likable as a rat in a bridle shop."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Every heart has its own hunger. Tell me yours."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "A gambler's luck is only predictable... when he's a cheat."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Bilgewater is a rough town to leave - I could make it easier for you."'

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Enemy) "A boxer who thinks with her fists must inevitably punch with her face."

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Child, why would you sublimate a hunger? Have you forgotten who you are?"

name: Tahm Kench
text: (Ally) "Do you want to reach your potential? It's a journey I could provide."

name: Tahm Kench
